val | work = ABC News | date = 2008-06-01 | accessdate = 2009-06-01 | url = http://abcnews.go.com/Video/playerIndex?id=4976468 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090601010834/http://abcnews.go.com/Video/playerIndex?id=4976468 | archivedate = 2009-06-01 | deadurl = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last = Raloff | first = Janet | title = Son of Furby | journal = Science News Online | date = 2008-05-30 | accessdate = 2008-12-01 | url = http://www.sciencenews.org/view/generic/id/32751/title/Science_%2B_the_Public__Son_of_Furby | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081201090631/http://www.sciencenews.org/view/generic/id/32751/title/Science_%2B_the_Public__Son_of_Furby | archivedate = 2008-12-01 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。《[[纽约邮报|纽约邮报]]》称，世界科学节在纽约文化领域的作用就像极客世界中的[[时装周|时装周]]和[[托尼奖|托尼奖]]<ref>{{cite news | last = Silverman | first = J. R. | newspaper = New York Post | date = 2008-05-30 | title = Science and the City | url = http://www.nypost.com/seven/05302008/entertainment/science_and_the_city_113055.htm | accessdate = 2008-11-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090531192157/http://www.nypost.com/seven/05302008/entertainment/science_and_the_city_113055.htm | archive-date = 2009-05-31 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>，[[科学频道|科学频道]]称赞科学节“鼓舞人心、信息丰富”<ref>{{cite journal | last = Scalera | first = Nicholas | title = Human, All Too Human | journal = Science Channel's Live Coverage of World Science Festival 2008 | url = http://blogs.discovery.com/world_science_festival/2008/06/human-all-too-h.html | date = 2008-06-01 | accessdate = 2008-11-25 | format = – <sup>[https://scholar.google.co.uk/scholar?hl=en&lr=&q=author%3AScalera+intitle%3AHuman%2C+All+Too+Human&as_publication=Science+Channel%27s+Live+Coverage+of+World+Science+Festival+2008&as_ylo=&as_yhi=&btnG=Search 学术搜索]</sup> | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080606064621/http://blogs.discovery.com/world_science_festival/2008/06/human-all-too-h.html | archivedate = 2008-06-06 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。